com.starsoft.plib.core.triggers

Enum NOT_NULL_DATA_STRATEGY


  • public enum NOT_NULL_DATA_STRATEGY

    Defines the strategy of behavior in case the task which takes the data from the previous task has a nonnull data

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • ALLOW

        public static NOT_NULL_DATA_STRATEGY ALLOW

        Accepts current data

      • REJECT

        public static NOT_NULL_DATA_STRATEGY REJECT

        Rejects data and throws an exception (default behavior)

      • CHANGE

        public static NOT_NULL_DATA_STRATEGY CHANGE

        Replaces data with data received from the previous task

      • ALLOW_IF_ERROR

        public static NOT_NULL_DATA_STRATEGY ALLOW_IF_ERROR

        Accepts the current data if the previous task failed with an error otherwise replaces the data
